    {
      "text": "After the war against the Divine Crusaders (DC) in Super Robot Wars III, many robots and their pilots began to disappear. When Masaki Andoh returns to \"Ragias Kingdom\", his homeland. However, he is shocked to find that the main goverment from his kingdom was eradicated by terrorists.",
